---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 487
  - Title: Qur’ân
    Location: II 257
Tags:
  - Combat-Action=Metanoia=Repentance, Renewal and Awakening
---
Allâh is the Protecting Friend of those who believe. He bringeth them
out of darkness into light. As for those who disbelieve, their patrons
are false deities. They bring them out of light into darkness.
